, 'Synergism', 'The risk of hepatic injury should be considered when brentuximab vedotin is used with other agents that are potentially hepatotoxic (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/291222/', '', 'Trimethoprim, Tamsulosin, Ascorbic acid, Hydroflumethiazide, Chlorothiazide, Lactic acid, Methazolamide, Amphotericin B, Clindamycin, Trichlormethiazide, Ciclopirox, More', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Panitumumab, Obinutuzumab, Bevacizumab, Necitumumab, Dostarlimab, Ramucirumab, Atezolizumab, Amivantamab, More', 1767369485);
